<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>EMMANUEL</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa nang locun, Zeitin nun hram ka thawk lai
 Hi Vaw-lei cung pi ah hin, Zeitin, ka nun khawh lai,
 Zeizong vialte ah, Na ka umpi lo ah cun
 Hi Vaw-lei nunnak ah hin, Tinhmi, ngei loin ka vakvai,

[C1]
   Oh! Jesuh Khrih
   Ka pawngah a ka umpi tu, Emmanuel,
   Ka nunnak cu, Nanglawng na si
   Nangmah he zungzal, Um ti peng ka duh,
   Na pekmi nunnak, thawngin kei ka nung
   Hngilh loin zungzal, a ka zoh khenhtu
   Emmanuel.
   Nanglawng na si
   Nangmah he zungzal, Um tti peng ka duh
   Na pekmi nunnak, thawngin kei ka nung
   Hngil loin zungzal, a ka zoh khenhtu
   Emmanuel.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
</song>